Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我有了点发现\N{\rEng}I found something
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,发现了什么？\N{\rEng}What did you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现了个地方\N{\rEng}I found a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那地方太大了\N{\rEng}It's massive in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.18,0:00:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,根本没完没了 看不到尽头\N{\rEng}It just goes on and on and on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,所有这些房间啊\N{\rEng}All these rooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地方建了它们\N{\rEng}this place built them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,其实更像是...\N{\rEng}Actually, more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,记得它们\N{\rEng}remembers them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.84,0:00:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,只不过记得越多\N{\rEng}And the more times it remembers something,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就越走样\N{\rEng}the less it does.
